I made this soup for Thanksgiving dinner, and, other than the desserts, it was far and away the guests' favorite dish. I made it the night before, so the yogurt was completely permeated with garlic and coriander.

Rating: 3
This is an absolutely delicious recipe, and very easy to make. I have made this soup five times, and I've gotten raves each time I've served it. I found that making the yogurt mixture several hours in advance added a much better flavor to the soup overall.

