I thought this soup might be a little like cream of mushroom. I was wrong. Instead it's like a big yam milkshake. I don't know if you can imagine what that tastes like. Try if it you're really curious. But be warned. It's weird.

Rating: 3
This was a hearty, tasty soup that was really easy to make. The garlicy yogurt was the perfect touch. I didn't have any cilantro, so I used mint in the yogurt instead, and it still worked just fine. A great soup for lunch on a brisk fall day.